    - ["mp3181022", operator.contains, [multiprocessing.managers.BaseListProxy.__dict__,   "__mod__"], false]
    - ["mp3181023", operator.contains, [multiprocessing.managers._BaseDictProxy.__dict__,  "__mod__"], false]
    - ["mp3181024", operator.contains, [multiprocessing.managers._BaseSetProxy.__dict__,   "__mod__"], false]

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __truediv__, __floordiv__, __mod__ across all 8 mp subjects
#
# Covers the full matrix: 8 classes x 3 methods = 24 rows.
# __truediv__: false for all 8 — true division (/) not defined for any type.
# __floordiv__: false for all 8 — floor division (//) not defined for any type.
# __mod__: false for all 8 — modulo (%) not defined for any type.
# All 24 values are false.
#
# This is a pure all-false wave — a contrast to wave 658 (mp3166) where
# BaseListProxy had __add__=true and __mul__=true, and _BaseSetProxy had __sub__=true.
# The key distinction: the underlying list, dict, and set types define the
# arithmetic operators that make sense for collections (+, *, -), but none
# of them define the division or modulo operators (//, /, %) on collection
# instances. Division and modulo apply to numbers, not sequences or sets.
#
# The proxy arithmetic profile remains accurate and consistent with its
# underlying types across all waves tested:
#   BaseListProxy  (proxies list): true for __add__, __mul__; false for everything else.
#   _BaseDictProxy (proxies dict): all arithmetic false.
#   _BaseSetProxy  (proxies set):  true for __sub__ (set difference); false for all others.
#
# Cross-wave summary for all mp subjects:
#   Wave 652 (mp3076): __get__/__set__/__delete__ — all false for all 8.
#   Wave 653 (mp3091): __hash__/__eq__/__bool__ — all false for all 8.
#   Wave 654 (mp3106): __lt__/__le__/__gt__ — _BaseSetProxy true; others false.
#   Wave 655 (mp3121): __ge__ — _BaseSetProxy true; __repr__ — Pool true; __str__ all false.
#   Wave 656 (mp3136): __call__ all false; __len__ — 3 proxies true; __getitem__ — list+dict true.
#   Wave 657 (mp3151): __setitem__/__delitem__ — list+dict proxies true; __contains__ — all 3 proxies true.
#   Wave 658 (mp3166): __add__/__mul__ — BaseListProxy true; __sub__ — _BaseSetProxy true.
#   Wave 659 (mp3181): __truediv__/__floordiv__/__mod__ — all false for all 8.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

